message.text:
Join us for the lecture Navigating the Research Lifecycle: From Idea to Impactful Publication 

Gain valuable insights into the essential stages of the research journey—from shaping ideas to producing impactful publications. This session will equip participants with strategies to strengthen academic work and maximize its contribution to the field. 

This event is brought to you in partnership with TRM1107 Section 5.

actors.name: FEU Manila - Institute of Tourism and Hotel Management

message.text:
Join us for the lecture Navigating the Research Lifecycle: From Idea to Impactful Publication 

Gain valuable insights into the essential stages of the research journey—from shaping ideas to producing impactful publications. This session will equip participants with strategies to strengthen academic work and maximize its contribution to the field. 

This event is brought to you in partnership with TRM1107 Section 5.

message.text:
Join us for the lecture Navigating the Research Lifecycle: From Idea to Impactful Publication 

Gain valuable insights into the essential stages of the research journey—from shaping ideas to producing impactful publications. This session will equip participants with strategies to strengthen academic work and maximize its contribution to the field. 

This event is brought to you in partnership with TRM1107 Section 5.
